{% block content %}
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-center text-gray-900 mb-4">About Echo</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-center mb-4">
        Echo is an open-source, lightweight PHP framework built on Symfony HTTP components and the Twig template engine.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-center mb-4">
        Our mission is to provide developers with an elegant and efficient way to create web applications while maintaining simplicity and flexibility.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-center mb-4">
        By default, Echo uses Tailwind CSS for frontend development, allowing for rapid and responsive design.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-center mb-4">
        As an open-source project, Echo encourages contributions from developers around the world, fostering a vibrant community dedicated to innovation.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-center mb-4">
        To contribute, please visit our GitHub repository <a href="https://github.com/imustakim/echo" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">here</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-center">
        Join us in shaping the future of web development with Echo, where your voice matters!
    </p>
{% endblock %}
